_source.text: 1965 Austin-Healey 3000 Mark III BJ8 H-BJ8-L/30530 - sold for $79,750 The car shown here was described in August 2012 as "better than new from the factory" by Gerry Coker, the legendary former Healey Motor Company designer who styled the original Austin-Healey 100 and the subsequent Big Healeys.
